Bosse_Unknown Source_Status_Brotherly Lo: Determined to protect a brother-in-arms, and will take a blow for said brother should he be in a tight spot.
Bosse_Unknown Source_Status_Directional: All action direction requirements are nullified.
Bosse_Unknown Source_Status_Firesnaking_: Deemed the priority target for certain attacks by Red Hot.
Bosse_Unknown Source_Status_Watersnaking: Deemed the priority target for certain attacks by Deep Blue.
ContentDesc_Arkadion - Superschwergewich: Introducing themselves by devastating Tritails Training, the Xtremes have not only challenged you, but made matters personal. Professional surfers infamous for their dangerous stunts and destructive behavior, the duo harness the souls of storm divers in battle to manipulate the elements of fire and water. For the sake of your second and more, it's time you taught these gym-wreckers some manners.
Instancecontenttextdata_40730_Text: And they dance out of the way unharmed! Unbelievable!
Instancecontenttextdata_40733_Text: Oh no, they've been felled with a vengeance!
Instancecontenttextdata_40734_Text: And they're down! Can they recover from this?
Instancecontenttextdata_40736_Text: And they're back in action! Can they turn the tide!?
Instancecontenttextdata_44203_Text: My word, such scorn for the challenger!
Instancecontenttextdata_44205_Text: What fearsome flames! He's set the ring ablaze!
Instancecontenttextdata_44208_Text: Hey, save some fun for me!
Instancecontenttextdata_44209_Text: Deep Blue's lost his cool! He's tagging in!
Instancecontenttextdata_44210_Text: If there ain't a wave to ride, just make one yourself!
Instancecontenttextdata_44211_Text: Good gods, what an enormous wave!
Instancecontenttextdata_44212_Text: Bet you've never seen anything this gnarly!
Instancecontenttextdata_44213_Text: Ugh, what a drag! Let's do this together, bro!
Instancecontenttextdata_44214_Text: Both brothers have entered the ring! That's grounds for disqualification!
Instancecontenttextdata_44215_Text: They don't fight alone either, so it's only fair!
Instancecontenttextdata_44219_Text: Er, it seems the referee is allowing it... It's double trouble for the challenger!
Instancecontenttextdata_44222_Text: The brothers have triggered a fusion explosion! Truly, they're deadly when mixed!
Instancecontenttextdata_44223_Text: I've been saving this trick just for you!
Instancecontenttextdata_44224_Text: Brace yourselves, folks! The Xtremes are holding nothing back!
Instancecontenttextdata_44225_Text: I'm not finished with you yet!
